'''Ghil'ad Zuckermann''' ([[Tel Aviv]], [[Israel]], [[1 juñu]] de [[1971]]) (D.Phil., [[Oxford|Universidá de Oxford]]; Ph.D., [[Cambridge|Universidá de Cambridge]])<ref>[https://www.vividsydney.com/speaker/prof-ghilad-zuckermann Vivid Sydney (Light, Music and Ideas)], Speaker: Prof. Ghil'ad Zuckermann.</ref> es un escrebiol i filólogu de [[Austrália]], [[Itália]], [[Israel]] i [[Réinu Uniu]].

Es professol univelsitariu de [[lingüística]] ena [[Universidá]] de [[Adelaida]], [[Australia]].<ref>[https://www.pedestrian.tv/news/meet-the-aussie-lumbersexual-on-a-mission-to-make-your-beard-lustrous Meet Ghil'ad Zuckermann, master of 11 languages], Pedestrian TV.</ref><ref>[https://www.jewishnews.net.au/ghilads-indigenous-language-game-changer/79545 Ghil’ad’s Indigenous language game changer],  Shane Desiatnik, AJN, July 12, 2018.</ref>  
 
